He made nice money but the job was exhausting. He decided to move to Prague and find something less stressful. I had a job like that open but I wasn't going to hire him easily. This cutie had to work for it hard. Maybe too hard because he wasn't too excited by the whole experience. Once I was done with him, he had trouble sitting... Even though I tried to be gentle the whole time. And I am rarely this considerate and careful while fucking my virgin applicants.
title: Dirty Scout 206
